
<html>
    <% include ../partials/head %>
<body>
    <% include ../partials/scripts %>
    <% include ../partials/nav %>
    <div class="container">
        <form autocomplete="off"></form>
    </div>
    <div class="definitionSpace">
        <p>
            From:<br><select id="sourceLanguage">
                <option value="English">English</option>
                <option value="Japanese">Japanese</option>
            </select>
        </p>
        <p>
            To<br><select id="destinationLanguage">
                <option value="Japanese">Japanese</option>
                <option value="English">English</option>
            </select>
        </p>
        <p>Ex: Cat<input id="term" placeholder="Type your word or phrase to define here...">
        <p>Ex:<br />neko<br />ねこ<br />猫<textarea id="WordTranslation" placeholder="Translations go here..."></textarea></p>
        <p>
            Click 'record' to record the word!<br /><button id="startRecordingWord" onclick="startRecording(this);">record</button>
            <button id="stopRecordingWord" onclick="stopRecording(this);" disabled>stop</button>
            <ul id="recordingslist"></ul>
        </p>
        <p>Ex: <br />Ah! There is a cat!<br />あ！ねこがいますよ！<br />あ！猫がいますよ！<textarea id="SentenceTranslation" placeholder="Example sentences go here..."></textarea></p></p>
        <p>
            Click 'record' to record the example sentence!<br />
            <button id="startRecordingSentence" onclick="startRecording2(this);">record</button>
            <button id="stopRecordingSentence" onclick="stopRecording2(this);" disabled>stop</button>
            <ul id="recordingslist2"></ul>
        </p>
        <p>Ex: kitten = koneko,こねこ,子猫<input id="TranslatorNotes" placeholder="Enter miscellaneous notes here..."></p>
        <p>Ex: animals<input id="Tags" placeholder="Enter tags here, separated by commas. Example: food, shopping, slang, formal"></p>
        <p><button class="submitDefinition" id="submitWord">Submit</button></p>
    </div>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.12.4.js" integrity="sha256-Qw82+bXyGq6MydymqBxNPYTaUXXq7c8v3CwiYwLLNXU=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/scripts/translation.js"></script>
    <script src="/scripts/recorderFrontend.js"></script>
    <script src="/scripts/recorder.js"></script>
    <% include ../partials/footer %>
</body>
</html>
